					{
						"extra": false,
						"text": "Awake and arise, O ye slumbering nations!\nThe heavens have opened their portals again.\nThe last and the greatest of all dispensations\nHas burst like a dawn o&rsquo;er the children of men!",
						"type": "verse"
					},
					{
						"extra": false,
						"text": "The dream of the poet, the crown of the ages,\nThe time which the prophets of Israel foretold,\nThat glorious day only dreamed by the sages\nIs yours, O ye slumbering nations; behold!",
						"type": "verse"
					},
					{
						"extra": false,
						"text": "Oh, lift up your voices in song and in story.\nLet banners of peace in all lands be unfurled,\nFor truth, heaven-born, in its beauty and glory\nIs marching triumphantly over the world.",
						"type": "verse"
					}
