						"extra": false,
						"text": "Let earth&rsquo;s inhabitants rejoice\nAnd gladly hail the glorious hour;\nAgain is heard a prophet&rsquo;s voice,\nAnd all may feel the gospel&rsquo;s pow&rsquo;r.",
						"type": "verse"
