						"extra": false,
						"text": "A key was turned in latter days,\nA blessing to restore&mdash;\nA gift of charity and peace&mdash;\nTo earth forevermore.\nOur Father, we would turn our hearts\nTo those who seek thy face,\nGive hope and comfort to the poor\nIn mem&rsquo;ry of thy grace.",
