						"extra": false,
						"text": "To play this as a duet, one person plays the accompaniment, and another person plays the voice parts one octave higher.\n\nSee also&nbsp;<em>Hymns,</em>&nbsp;no. 302, for a simple version with the melody in the accompaniment.",
