					{
						"extra": false,
						"text": "Once within a lowly stable,\nWhere the sheep and oxen lay,\nA loving mother laid her baby\nIn a manger filled with hay.\nMary was the mother there,\nAnd the Christ that baby fair.",
						"type": "verse"
					},
					{
						"extra": false,
						"text": "God sent us this loving baby\nFrom his home in heav&rsquo;n above,\nAnd he came down to show all people\nHow to help and how to love.\nThis is why the angels bright\nSang for joy that Christmas night.",
						"type": "verse"
					}
