						"text": "If you don&rsquo;t walk as most people do,\nSome people walk away from you,\nBut I won&rsquo;t! I won&rsquo;t!\nIf you don&rsquo;t talk as most people do,\nSome people talk and laugh at you,\nBut I won&rsquo;t! I won&rsquo;t!\nI&rsquo;ll walk with you. I&rsquo;ll talk with you.\nThat&rsquo;s how I&rsquo;ll show my love for you.\nJesus walked away from none.\nHe gave his love to ev&rsquo;ryone.\nSo I will! I will!\nJesus blessed all he could see,\nThen turned and said, &ldquo;Come, follow me.&rdquo;\nAnd I will! I will!\nI will! I will!\nI&rsquo;ll walk with you. I&rsquo;ll talk with you.\nThat&rsquo;s how I&rsquo;ll show my love for you.",
