					{
						"extra": false,
						"text": "Over the winding trail forward we go.\nWestward ho, Westward ho!\nThe dangers are many; the wagons are slow.\nWestward ho, Westward ho!",
						"type": "verse"
					},
					{
						"extra": false,
						"text": "Often we&rsquo;re weary and laden with woe.\nWestward ho, Westward ho!\nAnd what we shall find ahead we do not know.\nWestward ho, Westward ho!",
						"type": "verse"
					},
					{
						"extra": false,
						"text": "Over high mountains and prairies we go.\nWestward ho, Westward ho!\nTo lands of new promise with hearts all aglow.\nWestward ho, Westward ho!",
						"type": "verse"
					},
					{
						"extra": false,
						"text": "<em>Optional ostinato</em>\nWestward ho! Westward ho! Westward ho! Westward ho!&nbsp;<em>(etc.)</em>",
						"type": "other"
					}
